data.title: Other Canberra Attractions : PACER
data.meta_description: BUSY Schools offer Year 11 and 12 students the opportunity to re-engage with education and complete school while getting a head-start into employment.
data.text:
While in Canberra your school is also encouraged to visit some of the other Canberra educational institutions such as:

National Carillion

National Film and Sound Archive (Media and Me program only)

National Arboretum

National Library of Australia

National Police Memorial

Royal Australian Mint

Magna Carta Memorial

Australian Institute of Sport

Canberra Deep Space Communications Centre

CSIRO Discovery Centre

Geoscience Australia

Questacon – The National Science and Technology Centre

Australian National Botanic Gardens

Black Mountain Tower – Telstra Tower

Canberra Glassworks Ltd

National Dinosaur Museum

National Zoo and Aquarium

Cockington Green

Canberra Museum and Gallery

Mount Ainslie Lookout

Floriade/Floriade Nightfest

Canberra International Sports and Aquatic Centre

Big Issue Classroom

Please note: Some of these attractions may charge a fee for schools to visit.

Institutions listed on this page will not count towards a rebate.
